Class Registration

java.lang.Object
models.Registration
public class Registration extends Object
Represents a registration for a housing project.

This class handles registration details:

  • Officer that registered
  • Registration status
  • Approval/rejection
  • ID of the project the officer registered for
  • Last updated timestamp for registration
This class encapsulates the details of the registration, including the officer responsible, the project being registered, the status of the registration, and approval/rejection details. The registration can be approved or rejected by a manager.
